foreign earned income exclusion (~$105,900 for 2019, IIR), and

3. I will need to file with the IRS regardless of what I do, which you can
help with, and there are a variety of exclusions and other strategies we
can use to further limit the amount of salary I can draw without being
taxed by the US.?

If these statements are all true then I'm ready to move forward. Paris told
me to ask you to confirm!

Many thanks,
Josh

